      skos:note "As of March 17, 2026, the B2C pivot extends the March 12 SMB pivot further: SMB was already a shift from enterprise, but B2C goes beyond SMB to include individuals building companies alone. Both Scarlet and Tony converged independently on this framing. Enterprise remains as the top tier but the primary go-to-market is individuals and small businesses. Tony's core argument: AI has made every individual their own team. The volume play is B2C — solopreneurs, consultants, small business owners who need structure for context and memory." .
  }
